The darker stairs~
A permanent gloom and shadow seems to lurk in this room, even with the light
you carry bringing it's spreading glow. There seems to almost be a presence
pushing the light in. You wonder what could be below to make a room in such
a place as this seem so evil. You barely catch sight of a door in the south
wall, heavily barred with crude looking iron, and covered with glowing
sigils shaped into the lead that seals it. The door seems to be the only
exit from this room, other than the stairs leading up.
~
