#19546
The cell~
Total darkness rules this room, and odd substances drip from walls that seem
to ooze the very essence of evil itself. In the center of the room lies a 
glowing force field, it's edges delineated by silver runes and lines forming
a mystic summoning and warding diagram. As you step farther into the room
the ward suddenly fades, it's magic broken. In horror, you look down and
see you have stepped across some kind of threshold of silver. Whatever was
held by that ward is now loose.
~
